{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/c3-afa-2017-jakarta-perhelatan-akbar-para-penggemar-anime/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"C3 AFA 2017 Jakarta: Perhelatan Akbar Para Penggemar Anime","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bulan Agustus telah tiba, yang artinya sebentar lagi akan digelar acara tahunan keren untuk para penggemar anime di Asia Tenggara: C3AFA alias yang lebih dikenal dengan nama “Anime Festival Asia” (disingkat AFA). Sejarah singkatnya, AFA pertama kali diadakan di Singapura pada tahun 2008, dan bertujuan menjadi sebuah “anime convention” alias pertemuan para penggemar anime yang ada di seluruh Asia Tenggara. Bermula dari Singapura, AFA kini juga digelar di Bangkok, Thailand serta Jakarta, Indonesia.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Selain menjadi tempat <em>trading</em> dan <em>showcase</em> barang <em>anime-related</em> yang sedang populer, AFA juga menjadi ajang kehadiran para bintang tamu yang merupakan figur penting di bisnis anime (seperti seiyuu alias pengisi suara karakter anime atau produser &amp; sutradara anime yang terkenal dengan karya mereka) serta para cosplayer professional yang menyemarakkan acara. AFA 2017 di Jakarta tahun ini digelar selama tiga hari dari tanggal 18-20 Agustus 2017. Dan dari informasi yang sedang beredar, AFA 2017 Jakarta bakal menampilkan beberapa aksi pertunjukan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Untuk fans berat Ciel dan Sebastian dari anime <em>gothic</em> keren “Kuroshitsuji”, kalian dapat mengunjungi AFA 2017 Jakarta dan menikmati tayangan eksklusif movie terbaru dari serial Kuroshitsuji/Black Butler ini di panggung AFA 2017 Jakarta. Akan ada juga penjualan pernak pernik ekslusif Kuroshitsuji di booth yang sama. Psst, ada juga booth serta penayangan anime “Kuroshitsuji / Black Butler : Book of the Atlantic</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12426\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12426\" data-attachment-id=\"12426\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/c3-afa-2017-jakarta-perhelatan-akbar-para-penggemar-anime/attachment/13-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/13-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Poster “Black Butler: Book of the Atlantic”. Sumber: crunchyroll.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Poster “Black Butler: Book of the Atlantic”. Sumber: crunchyroll.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/13-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/13-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12426\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/13-2.jpg\" alt=\"Poster “Black Butler: Book of the Atlantic”. Sumber: crunchyroll.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12426\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster “Black Butler: Book of the Atlantic”. Sumber: crunchyroll.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anime “Frame Arms Girl” juga akan muncul di AFA 2017  sebagai bagian dari <em>featured anime show</em>, lengkap dengan penjualan aksesories yang berhubungan dengan anime ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12429\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12429\" data-attachment-id=\"12429\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/c3-afa-2017-jakarta-perhelatan-akbar-para-penggemar-anime/attachment/14-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/14-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Poster “Frame Arms Girls”. Sumber: pinterest.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Poster “Frame Arms Girls”. Sumber: pinterest.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/14-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/14-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12429\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/14-2.jpg\" alt=\"Poster “Frame Arms Girls”. Sumber: pinterest.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12429\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster “Frame Arms Girls”. Sumber: pinterest.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">AFA 2017 juga kedatangan salah satu <em>seiyuu</em> anime terkenal, Ms. Rika Abe (pengisi suara Hresvelgr) untuk  berinteraksi dengan fans. Jadikan kesempatan emas ini untuk foto bareng dan mendapatkan tanda-tangan. Jadi jangan lewatkan kesempatan ini ya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12441\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12441\" data-attachment-id=\"12441\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/c3-afa-2017-jakarta-perhelatan-akbar-para-penggemar-anime/attachment/18-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/18-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Rika Abe. Sumber: Facebook AFA\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Rika Abe. Sumber: Facebook AFA&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/18-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/18-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12441\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/18-1.jpg\" alt=\"Rika Abe. Sumber: Facebook AFA\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12441\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rika Abe. Sumber: Facebook AFA</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Featured anime show lainnya adalah anime “Fate/Apocrypha” dan “Kemono Friends”. Keduanya ini merupakan anime populer dan memiliki fans yang banyak (mungkin kamu salah satunya?)</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12453\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12453\" data-attachment-id=\"12453\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/c3-afa-2017-jakarta-perhelatan-akbar-para-penggemar-anime/attachment/15-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/15-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fate/Apocrypha. Sumber: website AFA Jakarta 2017\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fate/Apocrypha. Sumber: website AFA Jakarta 2017&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/15-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/15-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12453\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/15-3.jpg\" alt=\"Fate/Apocrypha. Sumber: website AFA Jakarta 2017\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12453\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fate/Apocrypha. Sumber: website AFA Jakarta 2017</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Akan ada juga penayangan/<em>screening</em> anime “Kuroko’s Basketball The Movie: LAST GAME” yang pastinya akan membuat fans kegirangan. Jadi pastiin kamu hadir disana. Tayangan lain yang bakal muncul meramaikan AFA 2017 Jakarta adalah <strong>“Hatsune Miku Expo 2016 Japan Tour”</strong> yang berlangsung di 5 kota dan berakhir di Tokyo, Jepang. Kalau kamu penggemar J-Pop Culture tentunya sudah tahu siapa itu Hatsune Miku, virtual idol ciptaan Crypton &amp; Sega yang sudah mengguncang dunia dengan penampilan dan kecanggihan audio visual “Vocaloid” mereka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12435\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12435\" data-attachment-id=\"12435\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/c3-afa-2017-jakarta-perhelatan-akbar-para-penggemar-anime/attachment/16-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/16-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Poster Miku Expo 2016. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Poster Miku Expo 2016. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/16-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/16-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12435\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/16-1.jpg\" alt=\"Poster Miku Expo 2016. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12435\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster Miku Expo 2016. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dan yang menjadi salah satu <em>staple</em> alias ciri khas serta selalu ditunggu-tunggu dari setiap acara AFA yang digelar adalah event “I Love Anisong”; yaitu mini konser lagu-lagu bertema anime yang diisi oleh bintang-bintang populer di jagat anime Jepang. Di AFA 2017 Jakarta ini, para bintang solo maupun band terkenal Jepang sudah siap untuk mengguncang Jakarta dengan pertunjukan mereka. Nama-nama yang akan muncul antara lain:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fhána</li>\n<li>Konomi Suzuki</li>\n<li>May’n</li>\n<li>Tomohisa Sako</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mereka akan mengisi “I Love Anisong” pada tanggal 19 Agustus 2017 hari Sabtu. Sementara untuk yang tanggal 20 Agustus 2017 hari Minggu, bintang yang akan mengisi acara adalah:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>KISIDAKYODAN AND THE AKEBOSIROCKETS</li>\n<li>Kradness</li>\n<li>Luna Haruna</li>\n<li>Shiena Nishizawa</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dan jangan lupa saksikan penampilan para cosplayer professional yang akan ngeramein acara AFA 2017 Jakarta nanti! Seperti Ying Tze dari Malaysia, Enako dari Jepang, DD-Tenka dari China, M.G dari Hong Kong, serta duo cosplayer pro dari negara kita, Clarissa Punipun &amp; Naru.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12438\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12438\" data-attachment-id=\"12438\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/c3-afa-2017-jakarta-perhelatan-akbar-para-penggemar-anime/attachment/17-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/17-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplayer Professional Naru dari Indonesia. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplayer Professional Naru dari Indonesia. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/17-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/17-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12438\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/17-1.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplayer Professional Naru dari Indonesia. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12438\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplayer Professional Naru dari Indonesia. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_12444\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-12444\" data-attachment-id=\"12444\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/c3-afa-2017-jakarta-perhelatan-akbar-para-penggemar-anime/attachment/19-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/19-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplayer Professional Ying Tze dari Malaysia. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplayer Professional Ying Tze dari Malaysia. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/19-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/19-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-12444\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/19-1.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplayer Professional Ying Tze dari Malaysia. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-12444\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplayer Professional Ying Tze dari Malaysia. Sumber: website AFA 2017 Jakarta</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Menurut situs resminya , acara AFA 2017 akan berlangsung di <em>venue </em>Jakarta International Expo. Info lebih <em>detail</em> (termasuk pembelian tiket dan jadwal resmi acara) bisa kamu temukan <a href=\"http://www.animefestival.asia/jakarta17\">disini</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sudah siap berpesta anime?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"c46fac4d-7c28-5349-9a1d-b979495410ee"}}}